OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPupils face 'lost decade'  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin education, MPs warn     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some pupils are facing a "lost decade" 
OL,6, of progress in schools in England if   
OL,7, action is not taken, MPs have warned.  
OL,9,FTheir report expressed alarm that it   
OL,10,Fcould take 10 years for the gap between
OL,11,Fdisadvantaged children and others to   
OL,12,Fnarrow to what it was before Covid.    
OL,14,FIt urged the government to take faster 
OL,15,Fand more effective action, such as     
OL,16,Fimproving uptake of a tutoring scheme  
OL,17,Fdesigned to help students catch up.    
OL,19,FThe government said it had made #5bn   
OL,20,Favailable for education recovery.      
